CustomField.description: The ID of the Name field that is dynamically generated in this org, can be found via source view when creating a new Relationship or in the URL when using the 'New Relationships' button. Populating this value will allow the field to pre-populate when creating new Relationships from the Relationship Viewer
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Populating this value will allow the field to pre-populate when creating new Relationships from the Relationship Viewer (see description for more information)
CustomField.label: Relationship Name Field Id
